# 🚀 CodSoft Internship Projects

This repository contains all the tasks completed during my virtual internship at CodSoft. The goal of these projects is to improve my frontend development skills and gain hands-on experience by building real-world web applications.

---

## 📂 Projects

### 🔹 1. Personal Portfolio
A responsive portfolio website showcasing my skills, projects, and development journey.

### 🔹 2. Landing Page
A modern and clean landing page designed with a focus on UI/UX and responsive layout.

### 🔹 3. Calculator
A simple and interactive calculator built using JavaScript for basic arithmetic operations.

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML  
- CSS  
- JavaScript  

---

## 🎯 Internship Objective

- Strengthen frontend development fundamentals  
- Build real-world projects  
- Improve problem-solving skills  
- Gain practical development experience  

